headline: Johnson Controls wins up to $630M contract for building automation systems from US Army Corps of Engineers
summary: The three-year base contract award will result in the installation, maintenance and service of Johnson Controls’ Metasys building automation systems to provide HVAC, fire and utility monitoring.
